<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>Pi̱ki Chihowa chia ma! ƲIT86</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Pi̱ki Chihowa chia ma!
 Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke;
 Chiso ilbʋsha pia ka
 Et ish pi holitoblashke.

[V2]
 Chim ilhfiopak achukma
 Ish pi nukfoki pullashke;
 Pishno ak inli hokʋto
 E chithaiyana he keyu.

[V3]
 Pi̱ki chi holitopa ma!
 Okla ilbʋsha pia ka
 Et ish pi̱ nukha̱klokbano,
 E chim aiahni fehnʋshke.

[V4]
 Chihowa holitopa ma!
 Pi̱ chu̱kʋsh okpulo ʋno
 Isht ish pi̱ kanchi pulla cha,
 Chu̱kʋsh a̱hli ish pimashke.

[V5]
 Yakni paknaka ilʋppa
 Il ahanta moma hokʋt,
 Ilbʋshʋt pilli fehnʋshke;
 Auet ish pi apelashke.

[V6]
 Anumpa ilbʋsha yoka
 Pit e chim asihi̱hla kʋt,
 Chisʋs chia pulla kak o̱
 Chiakaiya pi bʋnnʋshke.</lyrics>
</song>